# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# These paths are intended for trusted internal or devops validation, not for the
# supported external `/api/**` contract.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Internal documentation - redirect to generated API docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

### Internal documentation - generated docs index
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs/index.html
Accept: text/html

### Internal documentation - OpenAPI contract JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs
Accept: application/json

### Internal documentation - OpenAPI contract YAML
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs.yaml
Accept: application/vnd.oai.openapi
